column149:
This holiday weekend dont forget to hit pause. 

A genuine pause - not a pause with a schedule, a long list of things to do, or entertaining family because its what you always do. 

Make it a pause that counts. 

Not doom scrolling, shopping or binge watching TV. 

Read, do something creative, meditate or take a walk in the country. 

Take a moment to calm down your nervous system. 

Reset. 

Your body , your mind and your soul will thank you for it.

#pause #restandrelax #timeout #bestill #meditate #yogainstructor #yogainspiration #mindfulness #mindful #destress #stressrelieving #mentalwellbeing #wellbeing
